{"tid":1413193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[人手置頂] 緊急！一對義士新人需要大家幫忙！","createTime":"2019-08-05T09:10:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T09:20:33.000Z","uid":68819,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"094b9bbce08195f7a83a31a7c65009fd137d44db","tid":1413193,"uid":68819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T09:10:02.000Z","msg":"大家都知道有對情侶喺728被捕被告暴動罪<br />\n佢地尋日就結左婚，小弟喺呢度祝佢地白頭到老，永結同心，好人一世平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如大家都留幾句祝賀說話比佢地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，小弟透過朋友得知一對義士搵緊一d好重要既野，今次有幸為義士出一分綿力出呢個post<br />\n<br />\n以下係由義士本人撰寫，小弟代post, 希望大家都幫手人手置頂，有料報料，無料轉發，亦歡迎大家喺facebook轉發<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請轉發：<br />\n<br />\n事主可認證身分<br />\n<br />\n急求下列影片或相以助辯護警方暴動檢控<br />\n<br />\n地點：西營盤西源里<br />\n<br />\n時間：728 18:45-19:15<br />\n<br />\n尋找兩名記者(其中一位係攝影師) 拍到頭三位人仕(一對情侶及一位小妹妹)被捕經過，特別係被警員從西源里經德輔道西帶回西區警署。<br />\n<br />\n請聯絡 TWHung2019@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\nTo the press who had covered 7.28 protest on HK Island:<br />\n<br />\nIf any doubt, we will provide our ID to prove our identity. <br />\n<br />\nPls help ID/get in touch with *two* journalists who were present at <br />\nLocation: Sai Yuen Lane, Sai Ying Pun <br />\nTime: 18:45-19:15 (28/7)<br />\n<br />\nThe two had filmed police's arrest of 3 persons (a couple &amp; a teenage girl) at Sai Yuen Lane. The 3 were later brought back to Western Police Station via Des Voeux Rd West.<br />\n<br />\nAny photos or videos taken at above location &amp; time may help in defending against rioting charges.<br />\n<br />\nIf you have any information, please email to TWHung2019@gmail.com <br />\n<br />\nThank you!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb6d0298ebd857ecbb3845a6048a7a01b9e94b34","tid":1413193,"uid":68819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T09:13:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a50626ffa12cd64596fb7aa381fddcc701999d0","tid":1413193,"uid":68819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T09:13:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f764a99e1961e78c8d98eef47e3020ead48b0f","tid":1413193,"uid":68819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T09:14:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f88fb8d3bc7ef5bc6947bbb31e2f83a076ac0aaf","tid":1413193,"uid":68819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T09:14:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f23fe4287827969c533596a78d832e38e9925ad9","tid":1413193,"uid":68819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T09:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"731261b32b43a9a5ea7eb45c08e516452e015214","tid":1413193,"uid":68819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T09:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3315538e40fca43856ad73b9e38294e216e6195","tid":1413193,"uid":68819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T09:15:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/n